OL,3,CWhich seven locations have been
OL,4,Cselected for government's new towns?
OL,6,FMinisters have selected seven
OL,7,Flocations for new towns to be built
OL,8,Facross the UK.
OL,10,FEach proposed location is expected to
OL,11,Fdeliver at least 10,000 homes, with
OL,12,Fseveral delivering more than 40,000.
OL,14,FThe new towns will feature
OL,15,Fneighbourhoods that people can easily
OL,16,Fget around without a car, shared green
OL,17,Fspaces and vibrant high streets, the
OL,18,FMinistry of Housing, Communities and
OL,19,FLocal Government said.
OL,21,FThe seven chosen locations are:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
