OL,3,CWhich seven locations have been
OL,4,Cselected for government's new towns?
OL,6,FOf these locations, Tempsford, which
OL,7,Fis currently home to just 600 people,
OL,8,Fis likely to be the most controversial.
OL,10,FThe Government also assessed six other
OL,11,Flocations - Adlington, Heyford Park,
OL,12,FMarlcombe, Plymouth, South Barking and
OL,13,FWychavon Town ` but decided they will
OL,14,Fnot be taken forward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
