OL,3,CWhich seven locations have been
OL,4,Cselected for government's new towns?
OL,6,FAmong the names the government might
OL,7,Fcall these news towns are
OL,8,FElizabethtown (after the Queen),
OL,9,FPankhurst (after suffragette
OL,10,FEmmeline), Attleeton (after ex-PM),
OL,11,FAthelstan (first King of England) and
OL,12,FSeacole (after nurse Mary), the Times
OL,13,Freported.
