OL,3,CWhich seven locations have been
OL,4,Cselected for government's new towns?
OL,6,F"From the ground up, we're planning
OL,7,Fwhole communities with homes, jobs,
OL,8,Ftransport links and green spaces
OL,9,Fdesigned together ` so we can give
OL,10,Ffamilies the security and
OL,11,Fopportunities they deserve."
